response.overview: Jen and a group of friends set out to hike the Appalachian Trail. Despite warnings to stick to the trail, the hikers stray off course—and cross into land inhabited by The Foundation, a hidden community of mountain dwellers who use deadly means to protect their way of life.
response.title: Wrong Turn

results.name: WRONG TURN (2021) | UK Trailer | Horror | Starring Charlotte Vega & Matthew Modine
